</script>
</div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-references" ><h2 class="pane-title"> References</h2><div class="pane-content"><div class="field field-name-field-references field-type-link-field field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/for-the-press/2cf176e8/interactions-between-flu-subtypes-predict-epidemic-severity-more-than-virus-evolution" rel="nofollow">Interactions between flu subtypes predict epidemic severity more than virus evolution</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="actions-region"><div class="panel-pane pane-custom-pagers-pane" ><div class="pane-content"><ul class="custom-pager custom-pager-bottom"><li class="previous"> <span class="custom-pager-title">Previous</span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span> <a href="/articles/interviews/how-does-aphantasia-affect-autobiographical-memory">How does aphantasia affect autobiographical memory?</a></li><li class="next"> <span class="custom-pager-title">Next</span> <a href="/articles/interviews/4d-brain-map-pair-bonding">4d brain map of pair bonding</a> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-podcasts-panel-pane-3" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Related Content</h2><div class="pane-content"><div class="view view-podcasts view-id-podcasts view-display-id-panel_pane_3 view-dom-id-9238b9229ef367099010168dae9d9b89"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/articles/science-features">Science Features</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/science-features/what-flu-introduction-influenza" class="ajax-exclude">What is the flu: an introduction to Influenza</a></h4></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/articles/interviews/biology">Biology</a> | <a href="/articles/interviews/earth-science">Earth Science</a> | <a href="/articles/interviews/medicine">Medicine</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/interviews/why-colds-are-more-common-winter" class="ajax-exclude">Why colds are more common in winter</a></h4></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/podcasts/short">In Short</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/podcasts/short/covid-19-whats-happening" class="ajax-exclude">Covid-19: What&#039;s happening?</a></h4></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-4 views-row-even"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/articles/questions/medicine">Medicine</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/questions/why-flu-more-prevalent-winter" class="ajax-exclude">Why is &#039;flu more prevalent in winter?</a></h4></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-5 views-row-odd views-row-last"><div class="views-field views-field-term-node-tid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/articles/questions/medicine">Medicine</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/questions/was-bubonic-plague-worst-epidemic" class="ajax-exclude">Was the bubonic plague the worst epidemic?</a></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-node-comment-wrapper" ><div class="pane-content"><div id="comments" class="comment-wrapper comment-wrapper-nid-202240"><h2 class="title